snippet.title: Season 02 Launch Trailer | Call of Duty: Warzone & Black Ops 6
snippet.description:
The hunt is on in Season 02 of Call of Duty on January 28 🗓️

5️⃣ MP Maps - Bounty, Dealership, Lifeline, Bullet (Mid-Season), Grind (Mid-Season)
🔫 Fan-favorite Mode Gun Game returns
⚔️ New Weapons, Operators, Modes, and More
